panels.description: Shows the denied login attempts

targets.expr: topk(10, sum by (ip, username) (count_over_time({agent="fluentd",service="artifactory"} | json | log_source = "jfrog.rt.artifactory.access", action_response="DENIED LOGIN", username != "NA " [$__interval])))

panels.title: Denied Logins by User

panels.description: Shows denied actions by IP address

targets.expr: topk(10, sum by (ip, username) (count_over_time({agent="fluentd",service="artifactory"} | json | log_source = "jfrog.rt.artifactory.access", action_response=~"DENIED.*", action_response!="DENIED LOGIN", username != "NA" [$__interval])))

panels.title: Denied Actions by User

panels.description: Shows the top users by actions

targets.expr: topk(10, sum by (ip, username) (count_over_time({agent="fluentd",service="artifactory"} | json | log_source = "jfrog.rt.artifactory.access", username != "ntnustudentermonitor", username != "NA", username != "anonymous", username !~ "token.*", username != "_system_", username !~ ".*@.*" [$__interval])))

panels.title: Audit Actions by User

panels.description: Shows accepted deploys by user

targets.expr: topk(10, sum by (ip, username) (count_over_time({agent="fluentd",service="artifactory"} | json | log_source = "jfrog.rt.artifactory.access", action_response="ACCEPTED DEPLOY", username != "NA", username != "anonymous", username != "_system_" [$__interval])))
